</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-46_ pf-text-1">Best practice guidelines from credible sources such as the Resuscitation Council UK and the Health and Safety Executive outline the steps for providing first aid in diabetic emergencies, emphasising the importance of prompt assessment and intervention.





